content: <?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?> <metadata xml:lang="en"> <Esri> <CreaDate>20141016</CreaDate> <CreaTime>16333400</CreaTime> <ArcGISFormat>1.0</ArcGISFormat> <SyncOnce>TRUE</SyncOnce> </Esri> <dataIdInfo> <idAbs>This layer depicts the total number of fish sampling datasets (both linked and not linked to the NFHAP spatial framework) in the NFHP data system, per HUC12. Datasets include the "Multi State Aquatic Resources Information System" (MARIS, http://www.marisdata.org) dataset and the "NFHAP 2010 Community Fish Data Linked to Spatial Framework" dataset which was used in the 2010 NFHAP National Assessment. Some HUC's have data from none of the datasets, some have data from one of the datasets, and some have data from more than one of the datasets. </idAbs> <searchKeys> <keyword>USGS</keyword> <keyword>National Fish Habitat Partnership Program</keyword> <keyword>NFHAP</keyword> </searchKeys> <idPurp>This layer depicts the total number of fish sampling datasets</idPurp> <idCredit>U.S. Geological Survey, Core Science Analytics and Synthesis and Libraries, National Fish Habitat Partnership Program</idCredit> <resConst> <Consts> <useLimit/> </Consts> </resConst> <idCitation> <resTitle>nfhap_public_num_fish_sampling_datasets_per_huc12_all_datasets</resTitle> </idCitation> </dataIdInfo> <Binary> <Thumbnail> <Data EsriPropertyType="PictureX"></Data> </Thumbnail> </Binary> </metadata>
